title: How Should Britain and Europe Respond to Trump?
description: Bloomberg's Allegra Stratton, John Authers, Stephanie Baker and Francine Lacqua examine the global ramifications of the Trump presidency in a subscriber event held on March 11, 2025.  (Source: Bloomberg)
